Before generating or changing any UI in this project, read `DESIGN.md` at the project root.

Rules:
- Use ONLY the colors and tokens defined in DESIGN.md (Rosso Corsa #da291c, canvas #181818, elevated #303030)
- Sharp 0px corners on buttons and cards; uppercase CTAs with letter-spacing
- Inter as FerrariSans substitute; display weight 500, never bold headlines
- Match spacing from the 8px token ladder (4/8/16/24/32/48/64/96/128)
- Rosso Corsa is scarce — primary CTAs and key accents only
- No generic AI slop: no purple gradients, no pill buttons, no nested card grids
